{"type": "article", "id": 24242, "title": "翻开灯罩的极简桌灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-22T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105149h7RvdKxzeqw0ZAEk.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一盏极为简化的桌灯，它由一根长条形的柱子连接了圆片形的灯罩和底座。德国设计师 Simon Frambach 想要减少灯罩本身带来的阴影，于是设计成这种简化的结构。而圆片形灯罩本身就是一个可上下活动的开关，打开后灯光就慢慢出现，就像是翻开了笔记本电脑。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105147fFICkb8WugGhdj9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53952991\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105147B2HLea0n5YRbc4hu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 349px; width: 375px; left: 420px; top: 432px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105149EBksS4vQfRyxYlI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93162393\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}